<h2 id="why">Why support?</h2>

<p>
  convertFlow is a one-person project. It runs entirely in your browser — no servers,
  no accounts, no telemetry by default. That also means there's no upsell path,
  no premium tier, no enterprise SaaS waiting in the wings to subsidize it.
</p>

<p>
  Hosting is cheap (Cloudflare Pages) and the code is open. The expensive part is
  the time it takes to keep the format presets, embedding prices, and provider
  schemas current. Every dollar makes it easier to spend more of that time on the
  tool and less on a day job.
</p>

<h2 id="buy-coffee">Buy a coffee</h2>

<p>
  Smallest, easiest way. One-off contribution, no recurring charge, no account
  needed beyond a card.
</p>

<div class="cta-row">
  <a class="cta-primary" href="https://buymeacoffee.com/abhijathkat" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M3 6h8v4a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H6a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V6Z"/>
      <path d="M11 7h1.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 0 3H11"/>
